        <div class="col-6 about-content ms-5">
            <div class="col-5 col-md-12">
                <h3 class="about-heading mt-5">What we do</h3>
                <h6 style="margin-top:2rem;">
                    At Fannie Events, we are passionate about creating unforgettable events that leave a
                    lasting impression.
                </h6>
                <h6>
                    As a premier event planning company, we specialize in crafting unique
                    and exceptional experiences that surpass our clients' expectations.
                </h6>
                <h6>
                    With our meticulous
                    attention to detail, creative flair, and dedication to excellence, we bring your vision
                    to life, turning every event into a remarkable celebration.
                </h6>
                <h6>
                    Contact us today to discuss your event ideas and let us embark on a remarkable journey together!
                </h6>
            </div>
        </div>
