            <div class="col-12 col-md-12">
                <h3 class="about-heading mt-5">We value</h3>
                <h6 style="margin-top:2rem;">
                    <i>Creativity</i> We believe in the power of imagination and strive
                    to infuse creativity into every aspect of our event planning. From
                    innovative themes and awe-inspiring decor to unique entertainment
                    options, we go above and beyond to design experiences that are both extraordinary and memorable.
                </h6>
                <h6>
                    <i>Collaboration</i> We understand the importance of collaboration and work closely
                    with our clients to ensure that their vision is translated seamlessly into reality.
                </h6>
                <h6>
                    <i>Attention to Detail</i> We are obsessed with the details!
                    Our team meticulously plans and orchestrates every element
                    of your event, leaving no stone unturned.
                </h6>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-4 mt-5">
            <img src="/images-event/header5.jpg" height="500" />

        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="row col-12">
        <div class="col-6 about-content ms-5">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-12">
                <h3 class="about-heading mt-5">How we work</h3>
                <h6 style="margin-top:2rem;">
                    Fannie Events are proud to say that we have the ability to transform any space
                    into an environment where you feel welcomed and celebrated.
                </h6>
                <h6 style="margin-top:2rem;">
                    When we get the key details from you, we begin to prepare a uniquely curated event that is as
                    special as the people we serve.
                </h6>
                <h6 style="margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:5rem;">
                    We and our partners handles every thing about the event, that gives you an opportunity
                    to enjoy the moment, whithout lifting a finger.
                </h6>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-4 mt-5 mb-5">
            <img src="/images-event/header4.jpg" height="500" />

        </div>
    </div>
